    min/max(fixedWalls) = (0 0 0), (0 0 0)
writeCellCentres writeCellCentres1 write:
    writing cell-volumes field C to 10
    Writing the x component field of the cell-centres Cx to 10
    Writing the y component field of the cell-centres Cy to 10
    Writing the z component field of the cell-centres Cz to 10
writeCellVolumes writeCellVolumes1 write:
    writing cell-volumes field V to 10
yPlus yPlus1 write:
    writing field yPlus
    patch movingWall y+ : min = 0.223797, max = 0.223797, average = 0.223797
    patch fixedWalls y+ : min = 0.210739, max = 0.223797, average = 0.217072
zeroGradient zeroGradient1 write:
    UzeroGrad
    epsilonzeroGrad
    pzeroGrad
zeroGradient zeroGradient2 write:
    zeroGradient(U)
    zeroGradient(epsilon)
    zeroGradient(p)
End

